name: laccase
classes: Acting on diphenols and related substances as donors;
comment: A group of multi-copper proteins of low specificity acting on both o- and p-quinols, and often acting also on aminophenols and phenylenediamine. The semiquinone may react further either enzymically or non-enzymically.

references.title: The copper oxidases.
